      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 04:03:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国一年期债券收益率自 2009 年以来首次降至 1%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/china-one-year-yield-sinks-toward-1-as-policy-easing-bets-mount</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员加大对进一步放松货币政策的押注，且投资者寻求避险资产，中国一年期债券收益率自全球金融危机以来首次下滑至 1%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/china-one-year-yield-sinks-toward-1-as-policy-easing-bets-mount</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 01:34:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
